 consequences of authoritarianism and neoliberalism in Argentina.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aHorror filmszArgentinaxHistory and criticism. 4aFilm, Visual Culture, and Performing Arts : Film Studies. 4aLatin American, Caribbean, and Latinx Studies : Latin American Studies. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / History & Criticism.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package 2018z978311149142440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438470771423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438470771/original  a978-3-11-149142-4  SUNY Press eBook Package 2018b2018  aGBV-deGruyter-alles